Available on PS5® October 2, 2025.
Pre-order Now or Learn More: https://www.playstation.com/games/ghost-of-yotei/

snippet.title: Por Sus Besos - Tito Double P (Video Oficial)
snippet.description:
•ESCUCHA AQUÍ
https://orcd.co/porsusbesos

•LETRA:
Ay mama!
Tito doble P

Ya no se ni donde estoy
Le estoy marcando y me manda al buzón
Estaba en línea y ni me contestó
Su amiga me dice que ya se durmió
Pero no le creo nada
Siempre es la misma cuando anda tomada
Apaga el cel, dice que no pasa nada
y yo ando que me lleva la chingada

Por sus besos
Por su cuerpo
Por su voz
Por su tiempo
Por supuesto por su amor
¿Cómo es eso,
Que todo se te olvidó?
Ya ni siento
Traigo roto el corazón

Ay mama
Ahi te va chiquita
Y el balero mija?

Ya ni se pa donde voy
Sigo soñando con tu habitación
Que feo estar solo en el mes del amor
Y tú sigues sin contestar el fon
Solo en la madrugada
Que ando bien loco dice la plebada
Para dormir me haces falta aquí en mi cama

Hoy quiero que me lleve la chingada
Por sus besos
Por su cuerpo
Por su voz
Por su tiempo
Por supuesto por su amor
¿Cómo es eso
Que todo se te olvidó?
Ya ni siento
Tengo roto el corazón

Tito Double P
Spotify - https://spoti.fi/3RsDHUv
Instagram - https://bit.ly/3T cibEW
Apple Music - https://apple.co/3NdJn2u

•VIDEO
Dirección y Producción: Adán Ornelas Anta

snippet.title: Kelly Clarkson's Canceled Shows Explained: Attacks on Star 'Unfair' (Source)
snippet.description: Sources tell ET, Kelly Clarkson is facing unfair backlash over her Las Vegas concert, which she canceled just hours before the show. 'The attention Kelly is getting feels unfair,' one source says. 'One of the best things about Kelly is, she's a real person without a huge ego. She's had a lot going on in her personal life, and is doing her best to balance it all with her duties at [her talk] show (which is on hiatus right now, so not a factor). She's got to be a mom first, which a majority of the staff understands. She's been through a lot in the last couple years, but shows up with a good attitude, ready to do her best.'

snippet.title: T1 vs. GEN — MSI 2025 — Bracket Stage
snippet.description:
MSI 2025, LIVE FROM VANCOUVER #msi2025 

The 2025 League of Legends Mid-Season Invitational is here—bringing together the five regions to battle for glory, pride, and a critical edge heading into Worlds. As the second international showdown on the LoL Esports calendar, MSI pits two representatives from each regional league against one another in a high-stakes clash that tests their mettle at the season’s halfway mark. More than just a trophy is on the line: the winning team and the next best-performing region will earn extra slots at the World Championship, raising the stakes even higher. This year, the action unfolds beginning June 27 at the iconic Pacific Coliseum in Vancouver, Canada. Get ready for rivalries, redemption arcs, and unforgettable plays as pros will be challenged to Ignite The Fire Within.

PLAY-INS STAGE: June 27-June 29
BRACKET STAGE: July 1-July 12

You can always learn more and view the full match schedule at http://www.lolesports.com.

snippet.title: Jurassic World Rebirth Pitch Meeting
snippet.description:
Subscribe for more Pitch Meetings: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC9Kq-yEt1iYsbUzNOoIRK0g

It’s been more than one year since the final movie in the Jurassic World Trilogy, and therefore time for a soft reboot! Let’s swap in a different Marvel actor, mutate some dinosaurs and have some fun!

Jurassic World Rebirth definitely raises some questions. Like how many islands did these scientists have going? Why is their system designed to release all the dinosaurs at the slightest malfunction? Why was the family on the water, and why are they in this movie?

To answer all of these questions and more, step inside Ryan George’s Pitch Meeting for Jurassic World Rebirth!

Check Out These Other Videos:

Thunderbolts* Pitch Meeting
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MCks7E4Qa6k

Pitch Meeting Episode 400
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qNH2if9ymBE

#pitchmeeting #ryangeorge #jurassicworldrebirth #jurassicpark #jurassicworld #scarlettjohansson #jonathanbailey

snippet.title: Why Your Food is SO Expensive Now
snippet.description:
The REAL Reason Groceries Cost So Much
Use code johnnyharris at the link below to get an exclusive 60% off an annual Incogni plan: https://incogni.com/johnnyharris

Check out all my sources for this video here: https://docs.google.com/document/d/14TUklYgV2BM43NZ5GvwLSCO8MoWwNsxjasrRO4j_f5Q/edit?tab=t.0

The pandemic is over, but groceries are still more expensive than 2019. So we looked into how your food gets to you and why it costs more. 

Special thanks to:
- Groundwork Collaborative: https://groundworkcollaborative.org/
- ReFED: https://refed.org/
- International Fresh Produce Association https://www.freshproduce.com/

MORE CHANNELS:
Check out my new channel with Christophe Haubursin - Tunnel Vision  https://www.youtube.com/@christophe  
Check out my channel with Sam Ellis - Search Party  https://youtube.com/@SearchParty  

All the music for this video was created by our in-house composer Tom Fox and is available to license or just to listen to on our music channel Chromatic. Here's the soundtrack to this video: https://youtu.be/D7awDX0wNy4

Get access to behind-the-scenes vlogs, my scripts, and extended interviews over at https://www.patreon.com/johnnyharris

Do you have an insider tip or unique information on a story? Do you have a suggestion for a story you want us to cover? Submit to the Tip Line: https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdpNs1ykIwd7KNkwntN897X_SX9hJ8WiTH_erlLU_bQp2GGLg/viewform?usp=sharing

Get our World Map t-shirts now!

Tie Dye "World Map" shirt: https://store.dftba.com/products/world-map-t-shirt-tie-dye?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=product_shelf

I made a poster about maps - check it out: https://store.dftba.com/products/all-maps-are-wrong-poster

Custom Presets & LUTs [what we use]: https://store.dftba.com/products/johnny-iz-luts-and-presets

-- VIDEO CHAPTERS --

1:21 The History of Supply Chain
5:11 The Journey of Your Food
11:25 Why Food Is Getting So Expensive
23:45 Is There Hope?

Correction:
17:06 Publicly traded*

AI Disclosure:  Occasionally, we use AI to create some of the imagery in our videos, which our (very talented) animators then spend weeks developing into what you see in the final video. When AI is used to generate any imagery that may appear onscreen, we'll add this to the video description. We're learning as we go about AI usage and transparency, and appreciate your thoughts.

About: 
Johnny Harris is an Emmy-winning independent journalist and contributor to the New York Times. Based in Washington, DC, Harris reports on interesting trends and stories domestically and around the globe, publishing to his audience of over 5 million on Youtube.  Harris produced and hosted the twice Emmy-nominated series Borders for Vox Media. His visual style blends motion graphics with cinematic videography to create content that explains complex issues in relatable ways.

Джонни Харрис — независимый журналист, лауреат премии «Эмми», и автор статей для New York Times. -- वीडियो अध्याय --
0:00 खाना ज़्यादा महँगा है, है ना?
1:21 आपूर्ति श्रृंखला का इतिहास
5:11 आपके भोजन का सफ़र
11:25 भोजन इतना महँगा क्यों हो रहा है
23:45 क्या कोई उम्मीद है?

एआई प्रकटीकरण: कभी-कभी, हम अपने वीडियो में कुछ चित्र बनाने के लिए एआई का उपयोग करते हैं, जिन्हें हमारे (बेहद प्रतिभाशाली) एनिमेटर हफ्तों तक उस रूप में विकसित करते हैं जो आप अंतिम वीडियो में देखते हैं। जब एआई का उपयोग स्क्रीन पर दिखाई देने वाली किसी भी छवि को बनाने के लिए किया जाता है, तो हम उसे वीडियो विवरण में जोड़ देंगे। हम एआई के उपयोग और पारदर्शिता के बारे में सीख रहे हैं, और आपके विचारों की सराहना करते हैं।

के बारे में:
जॉनी हैरिस एक एमी पुरस्कार विजेता स्वतंत्र पत्रकार और न्यूयॉर्क टाइम्स के योगदानकर्ता हैं। वाशिंगटन, डीसी में स्थित, हैरिस देश और दुनिया भर में दिलचस्प रुझानों और कहानियों पर रिपोर्ट करते हैं, और यूट्यूब पर अपने 5 मिलियन से अधिक दर्शकों के लिए प्रकाशित करते हैं। हैरिस ने वॉक्स मीडिया के लिए दो बार एमी-नामांकित श्रृंखला बॉर्डर्स का निर्माण और मेजबानी की। उनकी दृश्य शैली मोशन ग्राफिक्स को सिनेमाई वीडियोग्राफी के साथ मिलाकर ऐसी सामग्री तैयार करती है जो जटिल मुद्दों को प्रासंगिक तरीकों से समझाती है।

ხელოვნური ინტელექტის გამჟღავნება: ზოგჯერ, ჩვენ ვიყენებთ ხელოვნურ ინტელექტს ჩვენს ვიდეოებში გამოსახულების შესაქმნელად, რომლის განვითარებასაც ჩვენი (ძალიან ნიჭიერი) ანიმატორები შემდეგ კვირებს ხარჯავენ საბოლოო ვიდეოში ნაჩვენები გამოსახულების გენერირებაზე. როდესაც ხელოვნური ინტელექტი გამოიყენება ეკრანზე გამოჩენილი ნებისმიერი გამოსახულების გენერირებისთვის, ჩვენ ამას ვიდეოს აღწერაში დავამატებთ. ჩვენ ვსწავლობთ ხელოვნური ინტელექტის გამოყენებისა და გამჭვირვალობის შესახებ და ვაფასებთ თქვენს აზრს.

ჯონი ჰარისი ემის მფლობელი დამოუკიდებელი ჟურნალისტი და New York Times-ის კონტრიბუტორია. ვაშინგტონში მოღვაწე ჰარისი საინტერესო ტენდენციებსა და ისტორიებს აქვეყნებს როგორც ქვეყნის შიგნით, ასევე მთელ მსოფლიოში, Youtube-ზე კი 5 მილიონზე მეტი აუდიტორიისთვის აქვეყნებს. ჰარისმა Vox Media-სთვის ორჯერ ემის ნომინანტი სერიალი „საზღვრები“ შექმნა და წამყვანი გახადა. მისი ვიზუალური სტილი აერთიანებს მოძრავ გრაფიკას კინემატოგრაფიულ ვიდეოგრაფიასთან, რათა შექმნას კონტენტი, რომელიც რთულ საკითხებს ადვილად ახსნის.

إفصاح عن الذكاء الاصطناعي: نستخدم الذكاء الاصطناعي أحيانًا لإنشاء بعض الصور في مقاطع الفيديو، والتي يقضي رسامو الرسوم المتحركة لدينا (الموهوبون جدًا) أسابيع في تطويرها إلى ما تراه في الفيديو النهائي. عند استخدام الذكاء الاصطناعي لإنشاء أي صور قد تظهر على الشاشة، نضيفها إلى وصف الفيديو. نتعلم مع تقدمنا ​​في استخدام الذكاء الاصطناعي والشفافية، ونقدر آراءكم.

جوني هاريس صحفي مستقل حائز على جائزة إيمي ومساهم في صحيفة نيويورك تايمز. يقيم هاريس في واشنطن العاصمة، ويقدم تقارير عن الاتجاهات والقصص المثيرة للاهتمام محليًا وعالميًا، وينشرها لجمهوره الذي يزيد عن ٥ ملايين على يوتيوب. أنتج هاريس واستضاف مسلسل "بوردرز" (Borders) المرشح مرتين لجائزة إيمي لشركة فوكس ميديا. يمزج أسلوبه البصري بين الرسوم المتحركة والتصوير السينمائي لإنشاء محتوى يشرح القضايا المعقدة بطرق سهلة الفهم.

The NBA 2K26 MyPLAYER Builder is already making noise, and in this video, we break down EVERYTHING we know so far — plus what it could mean for current NBA 2K25 players. From potential changes to attributes, badges, build types, and position restrictions, we dive deep into leaks, trends, and predictions for the next big evolution in 2K's most important feature.

Whether you're grinding in 2K25 or prepping for the future, this is your early look at how NBA 2K26's builder could shift the meta.

🎮 Inside This Video:
✅ Early breakdown of the potential 2K26 MyPLAYER Builder system
✅ Builder changes we NEED to see (based on past flaws)
✅ Possible badge & attribute overhauls
✅ Positional versatility & build balancing
✅ What to start preparing for NOW as a 2K25 player

snippet.description:
Christian Horner is GONE from Red Bull as the Formula 1 team's years of growing crisis have led to its biggest bombshell yet. 

Having led Red Bull for 20 years from its very first race in F1, Horner has been "released from his operational duties" - in other words, sacked as Red Bull Racing CEO and team principal.

And it's come as a real shock. So what's happened?

세계의 운명은 그렇게 제멋대로 결정된다.

Chúng ta đều biết, đây chính là quy tắc của thế giới.
Vậy cách làm của thần linh, rốt cuộc là xuất phát từ sự khinh miệt...
Hay xuất phát từ sự dè chừng bắt đầu vào một ngày nào đó?

th.title: [Genshin Impact บท Teyvat] ตัวอย่างคั่นฉาก - "ขีดจำกัดของเทพเจ้า" #GenshinImpact
th.description:
ในการประชุมของเหล่าทวยเทพ ไม่เคยมีเสียงของมนุษย์
ชะตากรรมของโลกจึงถูกตัดสินตามอำเภอใจเช่นนี้
พวกเรารู้ว่านี่คือกฎของโลก

ru.description:
На совете богов у смертных нет права голоса.
Так уж заведено, что судьбы мира определяют не люди.
Мы знаем, что таков порядок этого мира.

pt.title: Teaser de Interlúdio: "Capítulo Teyvat: Limitação do Divino" | Genshin Impact #GenshinImpact
pt.description:
Nenhuma voz humana é ouvida no conselho dos deuses.
E foi assim que, arbitrariamente, o destino do mundo foi determinado.
Sabemos que essa é a lei do mundo.
Mas os deuses agem por puro desprezo...
Ou será que em algum momento começaram a agir por medo?

de.description:
Bei den Besprechungen der Götter war noch nie eine menschliche Stimme zu vernehmen gewesen.
Und so wird von ihnen eigenmächtig über das Schicksal der Welt entschieden.
Wir wissen, dass dies die Regeln der Welt sind,

fr.title: [Genshin Impact · Teyvat] Aperçu de l'histoire - Intermède : « Les limites des divinités »
fr.description:
Au conseil des divinités, jamais une voix humaine ne se fait entendre.
C'est ainsi que le sort du monde fut déterminé.
Le monde est ainsi fait, tout le monde le sait.
Mais les divinités agissent-elles par mépris...

snippet.title: FLY vs. BLG — MSI 2025 — Bracket Stage
snippet.description:
MSI 2025, LIVE FROM VANCOUVER #msi2025 

The 2025 League of Legends Mid-Season Invitational is here—bringing together the five regions to battle for glory, pride, and a critical edge heading into Worlds. As the second international showdown on the LoL Esports calendar, MSI pits two representatives from each regional league against one another in a high-stakes clash that tests their mettle at the season’s halfway mark. More than just a trophy is on the line: the winning team and the next best-performing region will earn extra slots at the World Championship, raising the stakes even higher. This year, the action unfolds beginning June 27 at the iconic Pacific Coliseum in Vancouver, Canada. Get ready for rivalries, redemption arcs, and unforgettable plays as pros will be challenged to Ignite The Fire Within.

PLAY-INS STAGE: June 27-June 29
BRACKET STAGE: July 1-July 12

You can always learn more and view the full match schedule at http://www.lolesports.com.

snippet.title: The Truth About Kevin Durant's Nets Experience | LeBron James & Steve Nash | MIND THE GAME
snippet.description:
Kevin Durant is back for part 2 and he’s still dropping gems. In this conversation he tells LeBron James and Steve Nash why he fell in love with the game, how he earned respect on the court at a young age, and all about the achilles injury recovery process including his advice to Jayson Tatum, Damian Lillard, and Tyrese Haliburton.

Durant and Nash, his former coach on the Brooklyn Nets, share what exactly happened during their time together and why they weren’t able to fully reach their potential. Nash also gives sage advice to his counterparts on how to transition from your playing days to the next stage of life. 

Catch up with Part 1 of KD's guest appearance: https://youtu.be/VUzP2PvXeoY

Presented by UNINTERRUPTED and Wondery.

(0:00) - Intro
(1:11) - Why Ime Udoka (Houston Rockets) and Erik Spoelstra (Miami Heat) are special coaches
(12:30) - How KD fell in love with the game
(16:35) - KD on his mother believing in him
(19:20) - Why players have to be obsessed to be great
(25:53) - KD on every contract being a re-commitment to yourself
(30:45) - Steve’s perspective on retirement
(33:52) - KD’s achilles injury advice to Jayson Tatum and Damian Lillard
(38:07) - KD and Steve share what really happened in Brooklyn
(40:03) - Why Steve was unable to reach his full potential as Nets coach

New episodes drop every Tuesday. Watch Mind The Game with LeBron James and Steve Nash for NBA interviews, analysis, highlights and more. Subscribe to our YouTube Channel, watch on Prime Video or follow Mind The Game wherever you listen to podcasts.

Follow us on social:

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/mindthegamepod
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@mindthegamepod
X: https://www.twitter.com/mindthegamepod
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/mindthegamepod

snippet.title: I Quit.
snippet.description:
Hey, everyone. It's me, Quackity. I just want to share with everyone that I am approaching a new phase in my life. This video has been in the works for a long time, and I hope everyone can watch in it's entirety. Nearly three years ago I inadvertently quit my main platform where I was making content, and ever since then, I’ve been working on a lot of projects which I am incredibly proud of.

Today, I want to announce my biggest project yet.

Dababel.

This is a project which I hold very dear to my heart, not because of what it is, but because of what it represents to me. I was born and raised in Mexico, my native language is Spanish - and this gave me the opportunity to experience what it was like to be in another country and not know the language. Throughout my life and my career I’ve noticed how prevalent language barriers are - no matter where you are. And Dababel is a project with the objective to help people move beyond this barrier, which has existed since the beginning of time.

This is a project for you. This is a project for everyone.

DABABEL IS FOR THE WORLD. 

Thank you for all the support, and I hope you enjoy Dababel. To my global communities, to my new viewers and old, thank you for everything!

snippet.title: Everything David Corenswet Did To Become Superman
snippet.description:
_Superman_ star David Corenswet breaks down everything he did to become James Gunn’s adaptation of Kal-El in the latest _DC Studios_ cinematic universe installment. The American actor talks through every step of his journey to becoming Superman: from receiving the casting call during _Twisters_ filming to gaining 45lbs before shooting.

#DavidCorenswet #Superman #DCComics

00:00 - David Corenswet on becoming Superman
00:23 - Casting: “I’m not sure I really did want to play Superman”
08:13 - Research: “You need an imperfect humanity to have heroes”
10:25 - Training: “I was aiming for about 4,500 calories per day”
11:47 - Costume: “We could get out of the suit in about four-and-a-half minutes”
13:43 - Mannerisms: “I drew directly from All-Star Superman”

GQ recommends:

SpongeBob and his Bikini Bottom friends set sail in their biggest, all-new, can’t miss cinematic event ever…The SpongeBob Movie: Search for SquarePants. snippet.title: Timelapse shows Texas flash floods turn dry river into deadly rapids in 20 minutes
snippet.description:
Dramatic timelapse video shows how heavy rainfall turned a dry riverbed into surging rapids in just 20 minutes, as Texas was deluged by deadly flash floods on July 4.

CCTV footage shows water begin surging into the Llano River at 17:14. Within minutes, a road crossing the river is entirely submerged, with the waterline rising significantly on both sides of the riverbank and completely covering trees and bushes.

Watch more on Independent TV: https://tinyurl.com/yc7ukx9n

snippet.title: What next for Christian Horner, Max Verstappen and Red Bull? | The F1 Show
snippet.description:
► Subscribe to Sky Sports F1: http://bit.ly/SubscribeSkyF1
► Watch Sky Sports: https://bit.ly/BuySkySports

Simon Lazenby is joined by Ted Kravitz, Martin Brundle and Karun Chandhok for a special episode reacting to the news that Christian Horner has been sacked by Red Bull. We discuss what may have led to this decision, who is replacing him and what the future may hold for the Brit who has been at Red Bull since 2005. Also we hear from Craig Slater and David Croft who were on the ground at Red Bull's HQ.

pa.description:
**ਕੋਚ ਟਾਈਲਰ ਵਾਲ ਦੀ ਪਿਆਰ ਭਰੀ ਯਾਦ ਵਿੱਚ**

ਬਹੁਤ ਹੀ ਦੁਖ ਭਰੀ ਸੂਚਨਾ ਦੇ ਨਾਲ ਅਸੀਂ ਤੁਹਾਨੂੰ ਦੱਸ ਰਹੇ ਹਾਂ ਕਿ ਕੋਚ ਟਾਈਲਰ ਵਾਲ ਹੁਣ ਸਾਡੇ ਵਿਚ ਨਹੀਂ ਰਹੇ। ਕੋਚ ਵਾਲ ਇਕ ਬੇਮਿਸਾਲ ਇਨਸਾਨ ਸਨ, ਜਿਨ੍ਹਾਂ ਦੀ ਦਇਆਲਤਾ ਅਤੇ ਖੁਸ਼ਮਿਜਾਜ਼ੀ ਨੇ ਉਨ੍ਹਾਂ ਨੂੰ ਮਿਲਣ ਵਾਲੇ ਹਰ ਵਿਅਕਤੀ ਦੇ ਦਿਲ ਨੂੰ ਛੋਹ ਲਿਆ।
ਉਹਨਾਂ ਦੇ ਅਚਾਨਕ ਵਿਛੋੜੇ ਨੇ ਸਾਡੇ ਦਿਲਾਂ ਨੂੰ ਗਮੀ ਨਾਲ ਭਰ ਦਿੱਤਾ ਹੈ।

ਇਸ ਦੁਖਦਾਈ ਘੜੀ 'ਚ, ਅਸੀਂ ਕੋਚ ਵਾਲ ਦੇ ਪਰਿਵਾਰ ਨਾਲ ਸੰਪਰਕ ਕੀਤਾ
ਜਿਸ ਵਿੱਚ ਉਨ੍ਹਾਂ ਨੇ ਬਹੁਤ ਸਹਿਣਸ਼ੀਲਤਾ ਅਤੇ ਸਿਆਣਪ ਨਾਲ ਸਾਨੂੰ ਦੱਸਿਆ ਕਿ
ਟਾਈਲਰ ਚਾਹੁੰਦੇ ਸਨ ਕਿ ਉਨ੍ਹਾਂ ਦੀ ਆਸ ਅਤੇ ਸਕਾਰਾਤਮਕਤਾ ਭਰੀ ਸੋਚ ਲੋਕਾਂ ਤੱਕ ਪਹੁੰਚਦੀ ਰਹੇ, ਭਾਵੇਂ ਉਹ ਸਾਢੇ ਨਾਮ ਹੋਣ ਜਾਂ ਨਾ ਹੋਣ।

ਅਸੀਂ ਨਿਮਰਤਾ ਨਾਲ ਬੇਨਤੀ ਕਰਦੇ ਹਾਂ ਕਿ ਤੁਸੀਂ ਕੋਚ ਵਾਲ ਦੀ ਯਾਦ ਨੂੰ ਸਨਮਾਨ ਦਿਓ
ਅਤੇ ਇਸ ਮੁਸ਼ਕਲ ਸਮੇਂ 'ਚ ਉਨ੍ਹਾਂ ਦੇ ਪਰਿਵਾਰ ਦੀ ਨਿੱਜੀ ਜ਼ਿੰਦਗੀ ਦੀ ਇੱਜ਼ਤ ਕਰੋ।

ਕੋਚ ਟਾਈਲਰ ਵਾਲ ਦੀ ਹੌਂਸਲੇ ਅਤੇ ਦਿਲਾਸੇ ਭਰੀ ਵਿਰਾਸਤ
ਹਮੇਸ਼ਾ ਉਨ੍ਹਾਂ ਲੋਕਾਂ ਦੇ ਦਿਲਾਂ ਵਿੱਚ ਜੀਵੰਤ ਰਹੇਗੀ, ਜਿਨ੍ਹਾਂ ਨੂੰ ਉਹਨਾਂ ਨੂੰ ਜਾਣਨ ਦਾ ਸੌਭਾਗ ਮਿਲਿਆ।

ja.title: 45KG痩せたら、25万ドル獲得！
ja.description:
コーチタイラー ウォールを偲んで

コーチ　タイラー　ウォールが突然逝去されたという深い悲しみの知らせをお伝えいたします。
ウォール氏は、優しさと誠実さを持ち合わせた素晴らしい人物であり、彼と出会ったすべての人々に深い感動を与えてきました。その喪失は、私たちの心に大きな痛みを残しています。

கோச் டைலர் வால் அவர்களின் எதிர்பாராத மறைவுச் செய்தியை ஆழ்ந்த துக்கத்துடன் பகிர்ந்துகொள்கிறோம். கோச் வால் ஒரு அற்புதமான மனிதர், அவரது கருணையும் உண்மையான மனப்பான்மையும் அவரை அறிந்த அனைவரையும் கவர்ந்தது. அவரது இழப்பு எங்கள் இதயங்களை துயரத்தால் கனக்கச் செய்துள்ளது.

இந்தத் துயரச் செய்தியைத் தொடர்ந்து, இந்த வீடியோவை வெளியிட வேண்டுமா என்று கோச் வால் குடும்பத்தினரை அணுகினோம். அவர்கள், தங்கள் ஞானத்தோடும் பெருந்தன்மையோடும், டைலர் இல்லாத நிலையிலும் அவரது நம்பிக்கை மற்றும் நேர்மறையான செய்தி மற்றவர்களைச் சென்றடைய வேண்டும் என்று விரும்பியிருப்பார் எனத் தெரிவித்தனர்.

গভীর শোকের সঙ্গে আমরা জানাচ্ছি কোচ টাইলার ওয়ালের আকস্মিক প্রয়াণের কথা। কোচ ওয়াল ছিলেন একজন অসাধারণ মানুষ, যাঁর দয়া এবং আন্তরিকতা তাঁর পরিচিত সকলের হৃদয়ে ছাপ ফেলেছিল। তাঁর চলে যাওয়া আমাদের হৃদয়ে গভীর বেদনা রেখে গেছে।
এই দুঃখজনক সংবাদ পেয়ে আমরা কোচ ওয়ালের পরিবারের সঙ্গে যোগাযোগ করেছি যে, এই ভিডিওটি শেয়ার করা উচিত কি না। তাদের করুণা ও বিবেকবান মনোভাবের জন্য, তারা জানিয়েছেন টাইলার চাইতেন তাঁর আশাবাদী ও ইতিবাচক বার্তাটি অনেকে পৌঁছিয়ে যাক, এমনকি তাঁর অনুপস্থিতিতেও।

আমরা বিনীতভাবে অনুরোধ করছি কোচ ওয়ালের স্মৃতিকে সম্মান করুন এবং এই কঠিন সময়ে তাঁর পরিবারের গোপনীয়তার প্রতি শ্রদ্ধাশীল হোন।
কোচ টাইলার ওয়ালের করুণা ও উৎসাহের ঐতিহ্য তাদের হৃদয়ে জীবন্ত থাকবে, যারা তাঁকে চিনতে পেরেছেন।

snippet.title: Jay Leno's ULTIMATE GM Restomods: Buick, Chevy, & Oldsmobile! | Jay Leno's Garage
snippet.description:
Join Jay Leno in a special episode of Jay Leno's Garage as he showcases three incredible General Motors restomods that were built for SEMA, including a Hot Rod of the Year winner! With the invaluable help of GM engineers like Tony Roma, these classic American cars have been transformed into modern powerhouses while retaining their iconic styling.

1. The 1955 Buick Roadmaster: Jay recounts the personal history of his '55 Buick, from buying it out of the PennySaver to getting married in it. See how it was transformed with a 572 crate engine, C5 Corvette suspension, and disc brakes, making this vintage Buick able to "blow off a Corvette!" 

2. The 1932 Bowtie Deuce Roadster:

 Celebrating the 50th anniversary of the small-block V8, this '32 Chevy body sits on a '34 Chevy chassis and is powered by a 427 LS7 engine with 600 horsepower and a 6-speed manual gearbox. Discover the unique diamond-infused paint  and the challenges of building a classic hot rod with modern performance.

3. The 1966 Oldsmobile Toronado:

The Hot Rod of the Year winner in 2006, this Toronado is a true marvel. Originally a groundbreaking front-wheel-drive car , Jay's restomod features a custom chassis, a 427 LS7 engine with twin turbochargers , and over 1000 horsepower! Learn about its unique engineering, including custom-made wheels and a solid 50/50 weight distribution.

Experience these "bulletproof" builds, the challenges of working with extreme power, and the joy of driving these American legends!

nl-NL.title: Jay Leno's ULTIEME GM Restomods: Buick, Chevy en Oldsmobile! | Jay Leno's Garage
nl-NL.description:
Sluit je aan bij Jay Leno in een speciale aflevering van Jay Leno's Garage, waarin hij drie ongelooflijke General Motors restomods laat zien die speciaal voor SEMA zijn gebouwd, waaronder een Hot Rod of the Year-winnaar! Met de onschatbare hulp van GM-ingenieurs zoals Tony Roma zijn deze klassieke Amerikaanse auto's omgetoverd tot moderne krachtpatsers, met behoud van hun iconische stijl.

1. De Buick Roadmaster uit 1955: Jay vertelt over de persoonlijke geschiedenis van zijn Buick uit '55, van de aankoop uit de PennySaver tot zijn huwelijk erin. Zie hoe hij werd omgebouwd met een 572 kratmotor, C5 Corvette-vering en schijfremmen, waardoor deze vintage Buick "een Corvette kan overtreffen!" 2. De Bowtie Deuce Roadster uit 1932:

Deze '32 Chevy-carrosserie, die het 50-jarig jubileum van de small-block V8 viert, staat op een '34 Chevy-chassis en wordt aangedreven door een 427 LS7-motor met 600 pk en een handgeschakelde zesversnellingsbak. Ontdek de unieke diamantgeïnfuseerde lak en de uitdagingen van het bouwen van een klassieke hot rod met moderne prestaties.

3. De Oldsmobile Toronado uit 1966:

Deze Toronado, winnaar van de Hot Rod of the Year-prijs in 2006, is een waar wonder. Oorspronkelijk een baanbrekende auto met voorwielaandrijving, beschikt Jay's restomod over een aangepast chassis, een 427 LS7-motor met dubbele turbo en meer dan 1000 pk! Ontdek de unieke techniek, inclusief op maat gemaakte velgen en een solide 50/50-gewichtsverdeling.

Ervaar deze "kogelvrije" bouwwerken, de uitdagingen van het werken met extreme kracht en het plezier van het besturen van deze Amerikaanse legendes!

en.title: Jay Leno's ULTIMATE GM Restomods: Buick, Chevy, & Oldsmobile! | Jay Leno's Garage
en.description:
Join Jay Leno in a special episode of Jay Leno's Garage as he showcases three incredible General Motors restomods that were built for SEMA, including a Hot Rod of the Year winner! With the invaluable help of GM engineers like Tony Roma, these classic American cars have been transformed into modern powerhouses while retaining their iconic styling.

1. The 1955 Buick Roadmaster: Jay recounts the personal history of his '55 Buick, from buying it out of the PennySaver to getting married in it. See how it was transformed with a 572 crate engine, C5 Corvette suspension, and disc brakes, making this vintage Buick able to "blow off a Corvette!" 

2. The 1932 Bowtie Deuce Roadster:

 Celebrating the 50th anniversary of the small-block V8, this '32 Chevy body sits on a '34 Chevy chassis and is powered by a 427 LS7 engine with 600 horsepower and a 6-speed manual gearbox. Discover the unique diamond-infused paint  and the challenges of building a classic hot rod with modern performance.

3. The 1966 Oldsmobile Toronado:

The Hot Rod of the Year winner in 2006, this Toronado is a true marvel. Originally a groundbreaking front-wheel-drive car , Jay's restomod features a custom chassis, a 427 LS7 engine with twin turbochargers , and over 1000 horsepower! Learn about its unique engineering, including custom-made wheels and a solid 50/50 weight distribution.

Experience these "bulletproof" builds, the challenges of working with extreme power, and the joy of driving these American legends!

pl.description:

Dzięki nieocenionej pomocy inżynierów GM, takich jak Tony Roma, te klasyczne amerykańskie samochody zostały przekształcone w nowoczesne potęgi, zachowując jednocześnie swój kultowy styl.

1. Buick Roadmaster z 1955 r.: Jay opowiada osobistą historię swojego Buicka z 1955 r., od kupienia go od PennySaver po zawarcie w nim związku małżeńskiego. To nadwozie Chevroleta z 1932 r., upamiętniające 50. rocznicę silnika Small-Block V8, spoczywa na podwoziu Chevroleta z 1934 r. i jest napędzane silnikiem 427 LS7 o mocy 600 koni mechanicznych i 6-biegową manualną skrzynią biegów. hi.title: जे लेनो के बेहतरीन जीएम रेस्टोमोड्स: ब्यूक, शेवरले और ओल्डस्मोबाइल! | जे लेनो का गैराज
hi.description:
जे लेनो के गैराज के एक विशेष एपिसोड में जे लेनो के साथ जुड़ें, क्योंकि वे SEMA के लिए बनाए गए तीन अविश्वसनीय जनरल मोटर्स रेस्टोमॉड को प्रदर्शित करते हैं, जिसमें हॉट रॉड ऑफ़ द ईयर विजेता भी शामिल है! टोनी रोमा जैसे GM इंजीनियरों की अमूल्य मदद से, इन क्लासिक अमेरिकी कारों को उनके प्रतिष्ठित स्टाइल को बनाए रखते हुए आधुनिक पावरहाउस में बदल दिया गया है।

1. 1955 ब्यूक रोडमास्टर: जे ने अपनी '55 ब्यूक के व्यक्तिगत इतिहास को याद किया, इसे पेनीसेवर से खरीदने से लेकर इसमें शादी करने तक। देखें कि इसे 572 क्रेट इंजन, C5 कॉर्वेट सस्पेंशन और डिस्क ब्रेक के साथ कैसे बदला गया, जिससे यह विंटेज ब्यूक "कॉर्वेट को पीछे छोड़ने में सक्षम है!"

2. 1932 बोटी ड्यूस रोडस्टर:

छोटे-ब्लॉक V8 की 50वीं वर्षगांठ मनाते हुए, यह '32 शेवरले बॉडी '34 शेवरले चेसिस पर स्थित है और इसमें 600 हॉर्सपावर वाला 427 LS7 इंजन और 6-स्पीड मैनुअल गियरबॉक्स है। अद्वितीय डायमंड-इन्फ्यूज्ड पेंट और आधुनिक प्रदर्शन के साथ एक क्लासिक हॉट रॉड बनाने की चुनौतियों के बारे में जानें।

3. 1966 ओल्डस्मोबाइल टोरोनाडो:

2006 में हॉट रॉड ऑफ़ द ईयर विजेता, यह टोरोनाडो एक सच्चा चमत्कार है। मूल रूप से एक ग्राउंडब्रेकिंग फ्रंट-व्हील-ड्राइव कार, जे के रेस्टोमॉड में एक कस्टम चेसिस, ट्विन टर्बोचार्जर वाला 427 LS7 इंजन और 1000 से अधिक हॉर्सपावर है! कस्टम-मेड व्हील्स और एक ठोस 50/50 वजन वितरण सहित इसकी अनूठी इंजीनियरिंग के बारे में जानें।

इन "बुलेटप्रूफ" बिल्ड्स, अत्यधिक शक्ति के साथ काम करने की चुनौतियों और इन अमेरिकी किंवदंतियों को चलाने की खुशी का अनुभव करें! जे लेनो के गैराज से कार की देखभाल और डिटेलिंग की आपूर्ति खरीदें: https://www.lenosgarage.com/shine

id.description:
Bergabunglah dengan Jay Leno dalam episode spesial Jay Leno's Garage saat ia memamerkan tiga mobil General Motors yang luar biasa yang dibuat untuk SEMA, termasuk pemenang Hot Rod of the Year! Dengan bantuan tak ternilai dari para insinyur GM seperti Tony Roma, mobil-mobil klasik Amerika ini telah diubah menjadi mobil-mobil modern yang bertenaga sambil mempertahankan gaya ikoniknya.

1. Buick Roadmaster 1955: Jay menceritakan sejarah pribadi Buick '55 miliknya, dari membelinya dari PennySaver hingga menikah di dalamnya. Lihat bagaimana mobil itu diubah dengan mesin 572 crate, suspensi C5 Corvette, dan rem cakram, yang membuat Buick klasik ini mampu "melampaui Corvette!" 

2. Bowtie Deuce Roadster 1932:

Merayakan ulang tahun ke-50 mesin V8 blok kecil, bodi Chevy '32 ini berada di atas sasis Chevy '34 dan ditenagai oleh mesin 427 LS7 dengan tenaga 600 tenaga kuda dan transmisi manual 6 percepatan. Temukan cat unik yang diresapi berlian dan tantangan dalam membangun mobil hot rod klasik dengan performa modern.

3. Oldsmobile Toronado 1966:

Pemenang Hot Rod of the Year pada tahun 2006, Toronado ini benar-benar luar biasa. Awalnya merupakan mobil penggerak roda depan yang inovatif, restomod Jay menampilkan sasis khusus, mesin 427 LS7 dengan turbocharger ganda, dan lebih dari 1000 tenaga kuda! Pelajari tentang rekayasa uniknya, termasuk roda yang dibuat khusus dan distribusi berat 50/50 yang solid.

Rasakan pengalaman membangun kendaraan "antipeluru" ini, tantangan bekerja dengan tenaga ekstrem, dan kegembiraan mengendarai legenda Amerika ini!

ja.title: ジェイ・レノの究極のGMレストモッド：ビュイック、シボレー、オールズモビル！ | ジェイ・レノのガレージ
ja.description:
ジェイ・レノが司会を務める「ジェイ・レノのガレージ」特別エピソードでは、SEMAのために製作されたゼネラルモーターズ（GM）の素晴らしいレストモッド3台（ホットロッド・オブ・ザ・イヤー受賞車を含む）をご紹介します！トニー・ローマをはじめとするGMのエンジニアたちの惜しみない協力により、これらのクラシックアメリカンカーは、象徴的なスタイルを保ちながら、現代のパワフルなマシンへと生まれ変わりました。

1. 1955年式ビュイック・ロードマスター：ジェイが、ペニーセーバーで購入してから結婚式を挙げるまでの、愛車の55年式ビュイックの軌跡を語ります。572クレートエンジン、C5コルベットのサスペンション、そしてディスクブレーキを搭載し、このヴィンテージビュイックが「コルベットを圧倒！」するほどの車へと変貌を遂げた過程をご覧ください。

2. 1932年式 ボウタイ・デュース・ロードスター：

スモールブロックV8エンジンの50周年を記念したこの1932年式シボレー・ボディは、1934年式シボレー・シャーシに搭載され、600馬力の427 LS7エンジンと6速マニュアルギアボックスを搭載しています。ダイヤモンドを散りばめた独特の塗装と、クラシックなホットロッドに現代的なパフォーマンスを融合させたマシンを製作する難しさをご覧ください。

3. 1966年式 オールズモビル・トロネード：

2006年のホットロッド・オブ・ザ・イヤーを受賞したこのトロネードは、まさに驚異の逸品です。画期的な前輪駆動車だったジェイのレストモッドは、カスタムシャーシ、ツインターボチャージャー付き427 LS7エンジン、そして1000馬力を超えるパワーを誇ります。カスタムメイドのホイールや堅牢​​な50/50重量配分など、独自のエンジニアリングについて学びましょう。

これらの「防弾」ビルド、極限のパワーを扱う難しさ、そしてこれらのアメリカの伝説を運転する喜びを体験してください！

ジェイ・レノズ・ガレージでカーケア用品とディテーリング用品をお買い求めください：https://www.lenosgarage.com/shine

it.title: Le migliori Restomod GM di Jay Leno: Buick, Chevy e Oldsmobile! | Garage di Jay Leno
it.description:
Unisciti a Jay Leno in una puntata speciale di Jay Leno's Garage, che presenta tre incredibili restomod della General Motors costruite per il SEMA, tra cui una vincitrice del premio Hot Rod of the Year! Con il prezioso aiuto di ingegneri GM come Tony Roma, queste classiche auto americane sono state trasformate in moderni propulsori, pur mantenendo il loro stile iconico.

1. La Buick Roadmaster del 1955: Jay racconta la storia personale della sua Buick del '55, dall'acquisto da PennySaver al matrimonio a bordo. Scopri come è stata trasformata con un motore 572 a cassa, sospensioni da Corvette C5 e freni a disco, rendendo questa Buick d'epoca in grado di "spazzare via una Corvette!".

2. Bowtie Deuce Roadster del 1932:

Per celebrare il 50° anniversario del motore V8 small-block, questa Chevy del '32 è costruita su un telaio Chevy del '34 ed è alimentata da un motore 427 LS7 da 600 cavalli e cambio manuale a 6 marce. Scopri l'esclusiva vernice diamantata e le sfide che comporta costruire una hot rod classica con prestazioni moderne.

3. Oldsmobile Toronado del 1966:

Vincitrice del premio Hot Rod dell'Anno nel 2006, questa Toronado è una vera meraviglia. Originariamente un'auto rivoluzionaria a trazione anteriore, la restomod di Jay presenta un telaio personalizzato, un motore 427 LS7 con doppio turbocompressore e oltre 1000 cavalli di potenza! Scopri la sua ingegneria unica, inclusi i cerchi su misura e una solida distribuzione del peso 50/50.

Scopri queste build "a prova di proiettile", le sfide di lavorare con una potenza estrema e la gioia di guidare queste leggende americane!

de-DE.title: Jay Lenos ULTIMATIVE GM-Restomods: Buick, Chevy und Oldsmobile! | Jay Lenos Garage
de-DE.description:
Erleben Sie Jay Leno in einer Sonderfolge von „Jay Leno's Garage“, in der er drei unglaubliche Restomods von General Motors präsentiert, die für die SEMA gebaut wurden, darunter ein Hot Rod des Jahres-Gewinner! Dank der unschätzbaren Hilfe von GM-Ingenieuren wie Tony Roma wurden diese klassischen amerikanischen Autos in moderne Kraftpakete verwandelt, ohne dabei ihren legendären Stil zu verlieren.

1. Der Buick Roadmaster von 1955: Jay erzählt die persönliche Geschichte seines 55er Buick, vom Kauf aus dem PennySaver bis zur Hochzeit darin. Sehen Sie, wie er mit einem 572er-Kistenmotor, einem C5-Corvette-Fahrwerk und Scheibenbremsen umgebaut wurde, sodass dieser Oldtimer-Buick eine Corvette in den Schatten stellen konnte!

2. Der Bowtie Deuce Roadster von 1932:

Zum 50. Jubiläum des Small-Block-V8 sitzt diese 32er Chevy-Karosserie auf einem 34er Chevy-Chassis und wird von einem 427 LS7-Motor mit 600 PS und einem 6-Gang-Schaltgetriebe angetrieben. Entdecken Sie den einzigartigen Diamantlack und die Herausforderungen beim Bau eines klassischen Hotrods mit moderner Leistung.

3. Der Oldsmobile Toronado von 1966:

Dieser Toronado, Gewinner des Hotrod-Preises des Jahres 2006, ist ein wahres Wunderwerk. Ursprünglich ein bahnbrechendes Auto mit Frontantrieb, verfügt Jays Restomod über ein spezielles Chassis, einen 427 LS7-Motor mit zwei Turboladern und über 1000 PS! Erfahren Sie mehr über seine einzigartige Technik, einschließlich maßgefertigter Räder und einer soliden Gewichtsverteilung von 50/50.

Erleben Sie diese „kugelsicheren“ Konstruktionen, die Herausforderungen der Arbeit mit extremer Leistung und den Fahrspaß dieser amerikanischen Legenden!

ko.title: 제이 레노의 궁극의 GM 레스토모드: 뷰익, 쉐보레, 올즈모빌! | 제이 레노의 차고
ko.description:
Jay Leno's Garage 특별 에피소드에서 Jay Leno와 함께 SEMA를 위해 제작된 세 대의 놀라운 제너럴 모터스 레스토모드(Restomod)를 만나보세요. 그중에는 올해의 핫로드(Hot Rod of the Year) 수상 차량도 포함되어 있습니다! Tony Roma와 같은 GM 엔지니어들의 귀중한 도움으로 이 클래식 미국차들은 상징적인 스타일을 그대로 유지하면서 현대적인 파워풀한 차량으로 탈바꿈했습니다.

1. 1955년형 뷰익 로드마스터: Jay는 페니세이버(PennySaver)에서 구매한 1955년형 뷰익의 개인적인 역사를 이야기합니다. 572 크레이트 엔진, C5 코르벳 서스펜션, 디스크 브레이크를 장착한 이 빈티지 뷰익이 어떻게 "코르벳을 제압할 수 있을지" 직접 확인해 보세요!

2. 1932년형 보타이 듀스 로드스터:

스몰 블록 V8 엔진 출시 50주년을 기념하는 이 1932년형 쉐보레 차체는 1934년형 쉐보레 섀시에 탑재되었으며, 600마력의 427 LS7 엔진과 6단 수동 변속기를 탑재했습니다. 독특한 다이아몬드가 주입된 페인트와 현대적인 성능을 갖춘 클래식 핫로드를 제작하는 과정에서 겪은 어려움을 경험해 보세요.

3. 1966년형 올즈모빌 토로나도:

2006년 올해의 핫로드상을 수상한 이 토로나도는 진정한 경이로움을 선사합니다. 원래 획기적인 전륜구동 차량이었던 제이의 레스토모드는 맞춤형 섀시, 트윈 터보차저가 장착된 427 LS7 엔진, 그리고 1,000마력 이상의 출력을 자랑합니다! 맞춤형 휠과 견고한 50/50 무게 배분을 포함한 토로나도의 독특한 엔지니어링에 대해 알아보세요.

"방탄" 빌드, 극한의 파워를 다루는 도전, 그리고 이 미국의 전설적인 차량들을 운전하는 즐거움을 직접 경험해 보세요!

snippet.title: I'm taking a break my friends (After 58 years)!
snippet.description:
Well hello there, my dear friends! This video is a little different—no chef coat, no recipe, just a heart-to-heart. After 58 years in the kitchen and barely any breaks, I’ve finally decided it’s time to slow down and enjoy life beyond the sauté pan. So yes, I’m taking some time off! But don’t worry—Jack will keep things going while I soak up a little sunshine. Thank you for being part of this incredible journey. Your support means the world. I’ll be back soon, recharged and ready to cook something fabulous. In the meantime, enjoy the many recipes we’ve shared—and don’t forget your Mise-en-Place, my friends! Until next time…

localized.description:
Well hello there, my dear friends! This video is a little different—no chef coat, no recipe, just a heart-to-heart. After 58 years in the kitchen and barely any breaks, I’ve finally decided it’s time to slow down and enjoy life beyond the sauté pan. So yes, I’m taking some time off! But don’t worry—Jack will keep things going while I soak up a little sunshine. Thank you for being part of this incredible journey. Your support means the world. I’ll be back soon, recharged and ready to cook something fabulous. In the meantime, enjoy the many recipes we’ve shared—and don’t forget your Mise-en-Place, my friends! Until next time…

snippet.title: Search and recovery efforts continue across the flood ravaged Hill Country
snippet.description:
Flash floods in Texas killed at least 82 people over the Fourth of July holiday weekend and left others still missing, including girls attending a summer camp. The devastation along the Guadalupe River, outside of San Antonio, has drawn a massive search effort as officials face questions over their preparedness and the speed of their initial actions.

snippet.title: THIS PIZZA CHALLENGE IN FLORIDA HAS ONLY BEEN BEATEN ONCE! | BeardMeatsFood
snippet.description:
In this week's episode we're at Crostini's Pizza & Cuisine in Deltona, Florida having a crack at their 28" pizza challenge...

Teams of two get just 28 minutes in which to finish a 28" pizza (with toppings of their choice...or just plain cheese if you're feeling a bit soggy) and if successful, not only is the meal ON THE HOUSE but you get a $50 gift card for your troubles too! It's been a while since I tried a team pizza challenge, so I gave my old mate @WayneAlgenio a call to help me try to secure the win!

FOLLOW ME: @BeardMeatsFood

WATCH THE PODCAST: https://www.youtube.com/@BreakingBeardPod

FOLLOW THE PODCAST: @BreakingBeardPod

de-DE.title: DIESE PIZZA-HERAUSFORDERUNG IN FLORIDA WURDE NUR EINMAL BEWÄLTIGT! | BeardMeatsFood
de-DE.description:
In der Folge dieser Woche sind wir bei Crostini's Pizza & Cuisine in Deltona, Florida, und versuchen uns an der 28-Zoll-Pizza-Challenge...

Zweierteams haben nur 28 Minuten Zeit, um eine 28-Zoll-Pizza fertigzustellen (mit Belägen ihrer Wahl... oder einfach nur Käse, wenn sie etwas matschig ist). Bei Erfolg geht nicht nur das Essen AUFS HAUS, sondern ihr bekommt auch einen 50-Dollar-Gutschein als Belohnung! Es ist schon eine Weile her, dass ich an einer Team-Pizza-Challenge teilgenommen habe, also habe ich meinen alten Kumpel @WayneAlgenio angerufen, damit er mir hilft, den Sieg zu erringen!

fr-FR.title: Ce défi de pizza en Floride n'a été remporté qu'une seule fois ! | BeardMeatsFood
fr-FR.description:
Dans l'épisode de cette semaine, nous sommes chez Crostini's Pizza & Cuisine à Deltona, en Floride, pour tenter de relever leur défi pizza de 71 cm…

Les équipes de deux personnes ont seulement 28 minutes pour terminer une pizza de 71 cm (avec la garniture de leur choix… ou simplement du fromage nature si vous êtes un peu ramolli). En cas de réussite, non seulement le repas est offert par la maison, mais vous recevez aussi une carte cadeau de 50 $ pour vous récompenser ! Ça faisait longtemps que je n'avais pas tenté un défi pizza en équipe, alors j'ai appelé mon vieux pote @WayneAlgenio pour qu'il m'aide à remporter la victoire !

SUIVEZ-MOI : @BeardMeatsFood

hi.title: फ्लोरिडा में यह पिज़्ज़ा चैलेंज सिर्फ़ एक बार ही जीता गया है! | BeardMeatsFood
hi.description:
इस सप्ताह के एपिसोड में हम फ्लोरिडा के डेल्टोना में क्रॉस्टिनी के पिज्जा और व्यंजन में हैं, जहाँ हम उनके 28" पिज्जा चैलेंज का प्रयास कर रहे हैं...

दो लोगों की टीमों को 28" पिज्जा (अपनी पसंद की टॉपिंग के साथ... या अगर आपको थोड़ा गीलापन महसूस हो रहा है तो सिर्फ़ सादा पनीर) खत्म करने के लिए सिर्फ़ 28 मिनट मिलते हैं और अगर वे सफल होते हैं, तो न सिर्फ़ भोजन मुफ़्त में मिलेगा बल्कि आपको अपनी परेशानियों के लिए $50 का उपहार कार्ड भी मिलेगा! मुझे टीम पिज्जा चैलेंज आज़माए हुए काफ़ी समय हो गया है, इसलिए मैंने अपने पुराने साथी @WayneAlgenio को कॉल किया ताकि वे मुझे जीत सुनिश्चित करने में मदद कर सकें!

मुझे फ़ॉलो करें: @BeardMeatsFood

id.description:
Dalam episode minggu ini, kami berada di Crostini's Pizza & Cuisine di Deltona, Florida, mencoba tantangan pizza 28" mereka...

Tim yang terdiri dari dua orang hanya diberi waktu 28 menit untuk menghabiskan pizza 28" (dengan topping pilihan mereka...atau keju biasa jika Anda merasa agak lembek) dan jika berhasil, Anda tidak hanya akan mendapatkan makanan GRATIS, tetapi Anda juga akan mendapatkan kartu hadiah senilai $50 untuk usaha Anda! Sudah lama sejak saya mencoba tantangan pizza tim, jadi saya menelepon teman lama saya @WayneAlgenio untuk membantu saya mencoba mengamankan kemenangan!

it.title: QUESTA SFIDA DELLA PIZZA IN FLORIDA È STATA VINTA SOLO UNA VOLTA! | BeardMeatsFood
it.description:
Nella puntata di questa settimana siamo da Crostini's Pizza & Cuisine a Deltona, in Florida, per cimentarci nella loro sfida di pizza da 71 cm...

Le squadre composte da due persone hanno solo 28 minuti per finire una pizza da 71 cm (con ingredienti a scelta... o semplicemente formaggio semplice se la pizza vi sembra un po' molliccia) e, in caso di successo, non solo il pasto è OFFERTO DALLA CASA, ma si riceve anche una carta regalo da 50 $ per il disturbo! È da un po' che non provo una sfida di pizza a squadre, quindi ho chiamato il mio vecchio amico @WayneAlgenio per aiutarmi a vincere!

snippet.title: I Tried an Ultra Luxury Ritz Carlton Cruise
snippet.description:
Get started with Odoo today: https://www.odoo.com/r/ksR 
I’m getting onboard one of the world’s most luxurious cruise ships, the brand new Ritz Carlton Yacht, Ilma. I’ve booked a signature suite for the next 7 days, and I’ll be showing you everything this First Class ship has to offer. From the many restaurants (including a 10 course tasting menu for $700!), the pools, floating marina and we shall even take a look at the best room onboard, the owners suite. 

For reference as usual I paid in full for this cruise, as I don’t work with the cruise lines, to the tune of over $28,000 dollars! It’s actually not my first time onboard a Ritz Carlton Yacht, having tried their previous ship Evrima a couple of years ago. There were quite a few teething issues onboard that sailing, so I’m keen to see how they’ve changed (or if they have!) with the addition of Ilma and Luminara. These new ships are larger, with even more staterooms and facilities. As always do let me know what you think down below. 

0:00 - Intro
03:24 - My suite
07:07 - Fine Dining 
12:40 - Ship tour 
17:36 - The Marina
26:11 - Cost

fr-FR.title: J'ai essayé une croisière ultra luxueuse au Ritz Carlton
fr-FR.description:
Commencez à utiliser Odoo dès aujourd'hui : https://www.odoo.com/r/ksR
Je monte à bord de l'un des navires de croisière les plus luxueux au monde, le tout nouveau yacht Ritz Carlton, l'Ilma. J'ai réservé une suite signature pour les 7 prochains jours et je vous ferai découvrir tout ce que ce navire de première classe a à offrir : ses nombreux restaurants (dont un menu dégustation de 10 plats à 700 $ !), ses piscines, sa marina flottante et même la plus belle chambre du bord, la suite propriétaire.

Pour information, comme d'habitude, j'ai payé la totalité de cette croisière, car je ne travaille pas avec les compagnies de croisière, pour un montant de plus de 28 000 $ ! Ce n'est pas ma première fois à bord d'un yacht Ritz Carlton, ayant testé leur précédent navire, l'Evrima, il y a quelques années. J'ai eu quelques problèmes de démarrage lors de cette croisière, alors j'ai hâte de voir comment ils ont évolué (ou s'ils ont évolué !) avec l'arrivée de l'Ilma et du Luminara. Ces nouveaux navires sont plus grands, avec encore plus de cabines et d'équipements. Comme toujours, n'hésitez pas à me faire part de vos commentaires ci-dessous.

es-US.title: Probé un crucero de ultra lujo en el Ritz Carlton
es-US.description:
Empieza a usar Odoo hoy mismo: https://www.odoo.com/r/ksR
Me embarcaré en uno de los cruceros más lujosos del mundo, el flamante yate Ilma de Ritz Carlton. He reservado una suite exclusiva para los próximos 7 días y les mostraré todo lo que ofrece este barco de primera clase: desde los numerosos restaurantes (¡incluido un menú degustación de 10 tiempos por $700!), las piscinas, la marina flotante e incluso echaremos un vistazo a la mejor habitación a bordo: la suite del propietario.

Como siempre, pagué el total de este crucero (ya que no trabajo con las líneas de cruceros) por más de $28,000. De hecho, no es mi primera vez a bordo de un yate de Ritz Carlton, ya que probé su anterior barco, el Evrima, hace un par de años. Hubo bastantes problemas iniciales a bordo en esa travesía, así que estoy deseando ver cómo han cambiado (¡o si lo han hecho!) con la incorporación del Ilma y el Luminara. Estos nuevos barcos son más grandes, con aún más camarotes e instalaciones. Como siempre, cuéntenme qué les pareció abajo.

de-DE.title: Ich habe eine ultraluxuriöse Ritz Carlton-Kreuzfahrt ausprobiert
de-DE.description:
Starten Sie noch heute mit Odoo: https://www.odoo.com/r/ksR
Ich gehe an Bord eines der luxuriösesten Kreuzfahrtschiffe der Welt, der brandneuen Ritz-Carlton-Yacht Ilma. Ich habe für die nächsten sieben Tage eine Signature-Suite gebucht und zeige Ihnen alles, was dieses First-Class-Schiff zu bieten hat. Von den vielen Restaurants (inklusive eines 10-Gänge-Degustationsmenüs für 700 Dollar!) über die Pools und den schwimmenden Yachthafen bis hin zur Owners Suite, dem schönsten Zimmer an Bord.

Zur Information: Wie immer habe ich diese Kreuzfahrt komplett bezahlt, da ich nicht für Kreuzfahrten arbeite: über 28.000 Dollar! Es ist übrigens nicht mein erstes Mal an Bord einer Ritz-Carlton-Yacht, ich habe vor ein paar Jahren bereits das vorherige Schiff Evrima ausprobiert. Damals gab es einige Anfangsschwierigkeiten an Bord, daher bin ich gespannt, wie sich das Schiff mit der Ilma und Luminara verändert hat (oder ob es überhaupt welche gibt!). Diese neuen Schiffe sind größer und bieten noch mehr Kabinen und Einrichtungen. Wie immer könnt ihr mir unten eure Meinung mitteilen.

hi.title: मैंने अल्ट्रा लग्जरी रिट्ज कार्लटन क्रूज की कोशिश की
hi.description:
आज ही Odoo के साथ शुरुआत करें: https://www.odoo.com/r/ksR
मैं दुनिया के सबसे शानदार क्रूज जहाजों में से एक, बिल्कुल नए रिट्ज कार्लटन यॉट, इल्मा पर सवार होने जा रहा हूँ। मैंने अगले 7 दिनों के लिए एक सिग्नेचर सुइट बुक किया है, और मैं आपको इस फर्स्ट क्लास जहाज की हर सुविधा दिखाऊँगा। कई रेस्तराँ (जिसमें $700 में 10 कोर्स का टेस्टिंग मेन्यू भी शामिल है!), पूल, फ़्लोटिंग मरीना और हम जहाज पर सबसे अच्छे कमरे, ओनर्स सुइट पर भी नज़र डालेंगे।

हमेशा की तरह संदर्भ के लिए मैंने इस क्रूज के लिए पूरा भुगतान किया, क्योंकि मैं क्रूज लाइनों के साथ काम नहीं करता, $28,000 से ज़्यादा की राशि! यह वास्तव में रिट्ज कार्लटन यॉट पर मेरा पहला बार सवार होना नहीं है, मैंने कुछ साल पहले उनके पिछले जहाज एवरिमा को आज़माया था। उस नौकायन में जहाज़ पर कुछ शुरुआती समस्याएँ थीं, इसलिए मैं यह देखने के लिए उत्सुक हूँ कि इल्मा और ल्यूमिनारा के जुड़ने से वे कैसे बदल गए हैं (या क्या वे बदल गए हैं!)। ये नए जहाज़ बड़े हैं, और उनमें और भी ज़्यादा स्टेटरूम और सुविधाएँ हैं। हमेशा की तरह मुझे नीचे बताएँ कि आप क्या सोचते हैं।

nl-NL.title: Ik heb een ultra-luxe Ritz Carlton-cruise geprobeerd
nl-NL.description:
Begin vandaag nog met Odoo: https://www.odoo.com/r/ksR
Ik ga aan boord van een van 's werelds meest luxueuze cruiseschepen, de gloednieuwe Ritz Carlton Yacht, de Ilma. Ik heb een signature suite geboekt voor de komende 7 dagen en ik laat je alles zien wat dit eersteklas schip te bieden heeft. Van de vele restaurants (inclusief een 10-gangen proeverijmenu voor $ 700!), de zwembaden, de drijvende jachthaven, tot de beste kamer aan boord: de eigenaarssuite.

Ter referentie: zoals gewoonlijk heb ik deze cruise volledig betaald, omdat ik niet met rederijen werk, voor meer dan $ 28.000! Het is niet de eerste keer dat ik aan boord ga van een Ritz Carlton Yacht. Ik heb een paar jaar geleden hun vorige schip, de Evrima, geprobeerd. Er waren nogal wat kinderziektes aan boord van die cruise, dus ik ben benieuwd hoe ze zijn veranderd (of dat ze dat al zijn!) met de toevoeging van Ilma en Luminara. Deze nieuwe schepen zijn groter, met nog meer hutten en faciliteiten. Laat me zoals altijd hieronder weten wat je ervan vindt.

id.title: Saya Mencoba Pelayaran Mewah Ritz Carlton
id.description:
Mulailah dengan Odoo hari ini: https://www.odoo.com/r/ksR 
Saya akan naik ke salah satu kapal pesiar termewah di dunia, Ritz Carlton Yacht yang baru, Ilma. Saya telah memesan suite khusus untuk 7 hari ke depan, dan saya akan menunjukkan kepada Anda semua yang ditawarkan kapal Kelas Utama ini. Dari banyak restoran (termasuk menu mencicipi 10 hidangan seharga $700!), kolam renang, marina terapung, dan kita bahkan akan melihat kamar terbaik di atas kapal, suite pemilik. 

Sebagai referensi seperti biasa, saya membayar penuh untuk pelayaran ini, karena saya tidak bekerja dengan perusahaan pelayaran, dengan jumlah lebih dari $28.000 dolar! Sebenarnya ini bukan pertama kalinya saya naik Ritz Carlton Yacht, setelah mencoba kapal mereka sebelumnya Evrima beberapa tahun yang lalu. Ada beberapa masalah awal di atas pelayaran itu, jadi saya ingin melihat bagaimana mereka telah berubah (atau apakah mereka telah berubah!) dengan penambahan Ilma dan Luminara. Kapal-kapal baru ini lebih besar, dengan lebih banyak kabin dan fasilitas. Seperti biasa, beri tahu saya pendapat Anda di bawah ini.

pt-BR.title: Experimentei um cruzeiro ultraluxuoso no Ritz Carlton
pt-BR.description:
Comece a usar o Odoo hoje mesmo: https://www.odoo.com/r/ksR
Vou embarcar em um dos navios de cruzeiro mais luxuosos do mundo, o novíssimo Ritz Carlton Yacht, o Ilma. Reservei uma suíte exclusiva para os próximos 7 dias e mostrarei tudo o que este navio de Primeira Classe tem a oferecer. Dos diversos restaurantes (incluindo um menu degustação de 10 pratos por US$ 700!), às piscinas, à marina flutuante e até daremos uma olhada no melhor quarto a bordo, a suíte do proprietário.

Para referência, como sempre, paguei o valor integral deste cruzeiro, já que não trabalho com companhias de cruzeiro, no valor de mais de US$ 28.000! Na verdade, não é a minha primeira vez a bordo de um Ritz Carlton Yacht, tendo experimentado o navio anterior, o Evrima, há alguns anos. Houve alguns problemas iniciais a bordo naquela viagem, então estou ansioso para ver como eles mudaram (ou se mudaram!) com a adição do Ilma e do Luminara. Esses novos navios são maiores, com ainda mais cabines e comodidades. Como sempre, me contem o que acharam abaixo.

ja.title: 超豪華リッツカールトンクルーズに挑戦してみた
ja.description:
Odooを今すぐ始めましょう: https://www.odoo.com/r/ksR
世界で最も豪華なクルーズ船の一つ、最新鋭のリッツ・カールトン・ヨット「イルマ」に乗船します。これから7日間、シグネチャースイートを予約しました。このファーストクラスの船が提供するすべてをご案内します。数々のレストラン（700ドルの10コーステイスティングメニューを含む！）、プール、フローティングマリーナ、そして船内で最高の客室であるオーナースイートまでご紹介します。

ちなみに、私はクルーズラインと提携していないため、いつものように今回のクルーズ代金を全額支払いました。総額は28,000ドル以上です！実は、リッツ・カールトン・ヨットに乗船するのは今回が初めてではなく、数年前に前船の「エヴリマ」に乗船したことがあります。前回の航海では、船内でいくつか初期トラブルがありました。イルマ号とルミナラ号の増設で、どのように変わったのか（あるいは変わったのか！）とても楽しみです。新しい船はより大きく、客室や設備もさらに充実しています。いつものように、ぜひ感想をお聞かせください。

pl.title: Wypróbowałem rejs Ultra Luxury Ritz Carlton
pl.description:
Zacznij korzystać z Odoo już dziś: https://www.odoo.com/r/ksR 
Wsiadam na pokład jednego z najbardziej luksusowych statków wycieczkowych na świecie, zupełnie nowego jachtu Ritz Carlton Yacht, Ilma. Zarezerwowałem apartament firmowy na najbliższe 7 dni i pokażę Ci wszystko, co ten statek pierwszej klasy ma do zaoferowania. Od wielu restauracji (w tym 10-daniowego menu degustacyjnego za 700 USD!), basenów, pływającej mariny, a nawet przyjrzymy się najlepszemu pokojowi na pokładzie, apartamentowi właściciela. 

Jak zwykle zapłaciłem za ten rejs w całości, ponieważ nie współpracuję z liniami rejsowymi, w wysokości ponad 28 000 dolarów! Właściwie to nie jest mój pierwszy raz na pokładzie jachtu Ritz Carlton, ponieważ kilka lat temu wypróbowałem ich poprzedni statek Evrima. Na pokładzie tego rejsu było sporo problemów z ząbkowaniem, więc chętnie zobaczę, jak się zmieniły (lub czy się zmieniły!) po dodaniu Ilmy i Luminary. Te nowe statki są większe, mają jeszcze więcej kabin i udogodnień. Jak zawsze, dajcie mi znać poniżej, co o nich myślicie.

ko.title: 저는 리츠칼튼의 초호화 크루즈를 경험했습니다.
ko.description:
지금 바로 Odoo를 시작하세요: https://www.odoo.com/r/ksR
세계에서 가장 고급스러운 크루즈선 중 하나인 최신 리츠칼튼 요트, 일마(Ilma)에 탑승합니다. 앞으로 7일간 시그니처 스위트룸을 예약했는데, 이 퍼스트 클래스 크루즈의 모든 것을 보여드릴 예정입니다. 다양한 레스토랑(10코스 테이스팅 메뉴는 700달러!), 수영장, 수상 마리나, 그리고 최고의 객실인 오너 스위트룸까지 모두 살펴보겠습니다.

참고로, 저는 크루즈 선사와 거래하지 않기 때문에 이번 크루즈 요금을 전액 지불했는데, 총 2만 8천 달러가 넘습니다! 사실 리츠칼튼 요트를 타 본 건 이번이 처음이 아닙니다. 몇 년 전에 이전 배인 에브리마(Evrima)를 이용한 적이 있거든요. 그 당시에는 초기 문제가 꽤 많았는데, 일마와 루미나라(Luminara)가 추가되면서 어떻게 바뀌었는지(혹은 바뀌었는지!) 궁금합니다. 이 새로운 선박들은 더 크고, 객실과 편의시설도 더 많습니다. 언제나처럼 아래에 여러분의 생각을 남겨주세요.

it.title: Ho provato una crociera ultra lusso Ritz Carlton
it.description:
Inizia subito con Odoo: https://www.odoo.com/r/ksR
Salgo a bordo di una delle navi da crociera più lussuose al mondo, il nuovissimo Ritz Carlton Yacht, Ilma. Ho prenotato una suite esclusiva per i prossimi 7 giorni e vi mostrerò tutto ciò che questa nave di Prima Classe ha da offrire. Dai numerosi ristoranti (incluso un menu degustazione di 10 portate a 700 dollari!), alle piscine, al porto turistico galleggiante, e daremo persino un'occhiata alla migliore camera a bordo, la suite armatoriale.

Come al solito, ho pagato per intero questa crociera, dato che non lavoro con le compagnie di crociera, per un totale di oltre 28.000 dollari! In realtà non è la mia prima volta a bordo di un Ritz Carlton Yacht, avendo provato la loro precedente nave, l'Evrima, un paio di anni fa. Ci sono stati parecchi problemi iniziali a bordo di quella nave, quindi sono curioso di vedere come sono cambiati (o se lo sono cambiati!) con l'aggiunta di Ilma e Luminara. Queste nuove navi sono più grandi, con ancora più cabine e servizi. Come sempre, fatemi sapere cosa ne pensate qui sotto.

snippet.title: Floods devastate Texas hill country as death toll approaches 70
snippet.description:
President Donald Trump has approved federal disaster assistance for the state of Texas to assist in recovery efforts after massive floods destroyed dozens of homes and killed nearly 70 people. The funding is available to affected individuals in Kerr County, with assistance including grants for temporary housing and home repairs, low-cost loans to cover uninsured property, and various other recovery programs. Funding will also be available to state and local governments, as well as certain nonprofits, for emergency work and the repair of critical infrastructure, as well as the repair or replacement of facilities.

snippet.title: Alex Bowman on Bubba Wallace: "I Really Thought We Had Squashed Our Beef, but Clearly We Haven't"

snippet.title: How do Minecraft computers work?
snippet.description:
Today I learn to build Minecraft redstone computers, with expert lesson from Computational Redstone YouTuber  @mattbatwings   . Mattbatwings has built pacman in Minecraft, Super Mario Bros in Minecraft, Flappy bird in Minecraft and so much more - a lot of these giant redstone contraptions are featured in this video. Matt also does a tutorial on Computational redstone, covering the fundaments of Minecraft redstone logic, and even gets me to build my first computational redstone contraption.

MATTS CHANNEL: https://www.youtube.com/@mattbatwings
GO WATCH EVERYTHING HE HAS MADE!!

ja.title: Minecraft コンピューターはどのように動作しますか?
ja.description:
今日はMinecraftのレッドストーンコンピューターの作り方を、計算レッドストーンYouTuber @mattbatwings の専門的なレッスンで学びます。MattbatwingsはMinecraftでパックマン、スーパーマリオブラザーズ、フラッピーバードなど、数々の作品を作ってきました。この動画では、こうした巨大なレッドストーン装置がたくさん紹介されています。Mattは計算レッドストーンのチュートリアルも行っており、Minecraftのレッドストーンロジックの基礎を解説しています。さらに、私に初めての計算レッドストーン装置を作ってもらう機会を与えてくれました。

MATTSチャンネル: https://www.youtube.com/@mattbatwings
彼が作った作品は全部見てください！

id.title: Bagaimana cara kerja komputer Minecraft?
id.description:
Hari ini saya belajar membuat komputer redstone Minecraft, dengan pelajaran ahli dari YouTuber Redstone Komputasional @mattbatwings. Mattbatwings telah membuat pacman di Minecraft, Super Mario Bros di Minecraft, Flappy bird di Minecraft, dan masih banyak lagi - banyak dari alat-alat redstone raksasa ini ditampilkan dalam video ini. Matt juga membuat tutorial tentang redstone Komputasional, yang mencakup dasar-dasar logika redstone Minecraft, dan bahkan membuat saya membuat alat redstone komputasional pertama saya.

SALURAN MATTS: https://www.youtube.com/@mattbatwings
TONTON SEMUA YANG TELAH DIBUATNYA!!

fr-FR.title: Comment fonctionnent les ordinateurs Minecraft ?
fr-FR.description:
Aujourd'hui, j'apprends à construire des ordinateurs Redstone dans Minecraft, grâce aux conseils avisés du YouTubeur spécialisé en Redstone Computationnel @mattbatwings. Mattbatwings a construit Pacman dans Minecraft, Super Mario Bros dans Minecraft, Flappy Bird dans Minecraft et bien d'autres encore ; plusieurs de ces machines géantes en Redstone sont présentées dans cette vidéo. Matt propose également un tutoriel sur la Redstone Computationnelle, couvrant les fondamentaux de la logique de Redstone dans Minecraft, et me fait même construire ma première machine en Redstone Computationnelle.

CHAÎNE DE MATTS : https://www.youtube.com/@mattbatwings
ALLEZ REGARDER TOUT CE QU'IL A FAIT !

pt-BR.title: Como funcionam os computadores do Minecraft?
pt-BR.description:
Hoje aprendo a construir computadores redstone para Minecraft, com uma aula especial do YouTuber de Redstone Computacional @mattbatwings. Mattbatwings construiu o Pacman no Minecraft, o Super Mario Bros no Minecraft, o Flappy Bird no Minecraft e muito mais – muitas dessas engenhocas gigantes de redstone estão neste vídeo. Matt também faz um tutorial sobre redstone computacional, abordando os fundamentos da lógica de redstone no Minecraft, e até me faz construir minha primeira engenhoca computacional de redstone.

CANAL DO MATTS: https://www.youtube.com/@mattbatwings
ASSISTA A TUDO O QUE ELE FEZ!!

nl-NL.title: Hoe werken Minecraft-computers?
nl-NL.description:
Vandaag leer ik Minecraft redstone computers bouwen, met deskundige les van Computational Redstone YouTuber @mattbatwings. Mattbatwings heeft Pacman in Minecraft, Super Mario Bros. in Minecraft, Flappy Bird in Minecraft en nog veel meer gebouwd - veel van deze gigantische redstone-apparaten zijn te zien in deze video. Matt geeft ook een tutorial over Computational Redstone, waarin hij de basis van Minecraft redstone logica behandelt, en hij laat me zelfs mijn eerste computational Redstone-apparaat bouwen.

MATTS KANAAL: https://www.youtube.com/@mattbatwings
GA KIJKEN NAAR ALLES WAT HIJ HEEFT GEMAAKT!!

hi.title: Minecraft कंप्यूटर कैसे काम करते हैं?
hi.description:
आज मैं कम्प्यूटेशनल रेडस्टोन यूट्यूबर @mattbatwings से विशेषज्ञ पाठ के साथ Minecraft रेडस्टोन कंप्यूटर बनाना सीख रहा हूँ। मैटबैटविंग्स ने Minecraft में पैकमैन, Minecraft में सुपर मारियो ब्रोस, Minecraft में फ्लैपी बर्ड और बहुत कुछ बनाया है - इनमें से बहुत सारे विशाल रेडस्टोन उपकरण इस वीडियो में दिखाए गए हैं। मैट कम्प्यूटेशनल रेडस्टोन पर एक ट्यूटोरियल भी करता है, जिसमें Minecraft रेडस्टोन लॉजिक के मूल सिद्धांतों को शामिल किया गया है, और यहाँ तक कि मुझे अपना पहला कम्प्यूटेशनल रेडस्टोन उपकरण बनाने के लिए भी कहा।

मैट्स चैनल: https://www.youtube.com/@mattbatwings
जाओ और देखो कि उसने क्या-क्या बनाया है!!

pl.title: Jak działają komputery Minecraft?
pl.description:
Dzisiaj uczę się budować komputery z redstone'a w Minecrafcie, z ekspercką lekcją od YouTubera zajmującego się redstonem obliczeniowym @mattbatwings. Mattbatwings zbudował Pacmana w Minecrafcie, Super Mario Bros w Minecrafcie, Flappy Bird w Minecrafcie i wiele innych - wiele z tych gigantycznych urządzeń z redstone'a jest pokazanych w tym filmie. Matt robi również samouczek na temat redstone'a obliczeniowego, omawiając podstawy logiki redstone'a w Minecrafcie, a nawet sprawia, że ​​buduję moje pierwsze urządzenie z redstone'a obliczeniowego.

KANAŁ MATTA: https://www.youtube.com/@mattbatwings
OBEJRZYJ WSZYSTKO, CO ZROBIŁ!!

ko.title: 마인크래프트 컴퓨터는 어떻게 작동하나요?
ko.description:
오늘은 컴퓨테이셔널 레드스톤 유튜버 @mattbatwings의 전문가 레슨을 통해 마인크래프트 레드스톤 컴퓨터를 만드는 법을 배워봅니다. Mattbatwings는 마인크래프트에서 팩맨, 슈퍼 마리오 브라더스, 플래피 버드 등 수많은 게임을 만들어 냈으며, 이 영상에는 이러한 거대한 레드스톤 장치들이 많이 등장합니다. Matt는 또한 마인크래프트 레드스톤 논리의 기본을 다루는 컴퓨테이셔널 레드스톤 튜토리얼을 진행하고, 심지어 저에게 첫 번째 컴퓨테이셔널 레드스톤 장치를 만들어 보도록 돕습니다.

MATTS 채널: https://www.youtube.com/@mattbatwings
그가 만든 모든 것을 보러 가세요!!

it.title: Come funzionano i computer di Minecraft?
it.description:
Oggi imparo a costruire computer in redstone di Minecraft, con la lezione esperta dell'esperto YouTuber @mattbatwings specializzato in redstone computazionale. Mattbatwings ha costruito Pacman in Minecraft, Super Mario Bros in Minecraft, Flappy Bird in Minecraft e molto altro ancora: molti di questi giganteschi congegni in redstone sono presenti in questo video. Matt realizza anche un tutorial sulla redstone computazionale, che illustra i fondamenti della logica della redstone di Minecraft, e mi fa persino costruire il mio primo congegno in redstone computazionale.

CANALE DI MATTS: https://www.youtube.com/@mattbatwings
ANDATE A GUARDARE TUTTO CIÒ CHE HA CREATO!!

de-DE.title: Wie funktionieren Minecraft-Computer?
de-DE.description:
Heute lerne ich, wie man Redstone-Computer in Minecraft baut – mit einer Experten-Anleitung von @mattbatwings, einem YouTuber für Computational Redstone. Mattbatwings hat Pacman, Super Mario Bros, Flappy Bird und vieles mehr in Minecraft gebaut – viele dieser riesigen Redstone-Maschinen sind in diesem Video zu sehen. Matt bietet außerdem ein Tutorial zu Computational Redstone an, das die Grundlagen der Redstone-Logik in Minecraft erklärt, und bringt mich sogar dazu, meine erste eigene Redstone-Maschine zu bauen.


MATTS KANAL: https://www.youtube.com/@mattbatwings

SCHAUT EUCH ALLES AN, WAS ER GEMACHT HAT!

snippet.title: Death toll in central Texas flash floods rises to 79 as sheriff says 10 campers remain missing
snippet.description:
Families sifted through waterlogged debris Sunday and stepped inside empty cabins at Camp Mystic, an all-girls summer camp ripped apart by flash floods that washed homes off their foundations and killed at least 79 people in central Texas.

Rescuers maneuvering through challenging terrain continued their desperate search for the missing, including 10 girls and a counselor from the camp. For the first time since the storms began pounding Texas, Gov. Greg Abbott said there were 41 people confirmed to be unaccounted for across the state and more could be missing.

Read more at: https://www.9news.com/article/news/nation-world/texas-floods-campers-missing/507-2c41ffb5-638c-4d53-bc6b-a444a0618bdb

snippet.title: The evidence that damned Piastri in Verstappen British GP controversy
snippet.description:
A penalty for erratic driving decided the British Grand Prix as an aggrieved Oscar Piastri lost victory to McLaren team-mate and F1 title rival Lando Norris. 

This wet and wild Silverstone F1 race came down to one key moment: the restart on lap 21, when Piastri’s braking caught Verstappen out. Jon Noble and Scott Mitchell-Malm delve into the data that doomed Piastri.

00:00 How Piastri lost victory
01:43 Piastri's double trouble
03:10 Verstappen's view
04:17 Why Canada was different
05:40 McLaren suggests gamesmanship
07:48 Piastri's cheeky swap request
08:46 Title race implications 

READ MORE HERE: https://www.the-race.com/formula-1/why-oscar-piastri-got-race-costing-british-gp-f1-penalty-erratic-braking/

it.title: Iniziano i lavori in metallo sul camion di patate di Matt!
it.description:
I saldi del 4 luglio di onX Offroad sono ancora attivi! Ottieni il 50% di sconto sulla migliore app di mappatura sentieri in circolazione con il codice FOJ25 su http://onxmaps.com/offroad e sblocca oltre 1050.000 km di sentieri, campeggi e strumenti per avventure fuori dalla rete elettrica. Se ti iscrivi, invia un'e-mail a merchsupport@robbylayton.com e per ogni 5 $ spesi con onX, ti regaleremo un biglietto d'ingresso per partecipare all'estrazione della C10 del '72! Il denaro per ogni ordine è ancora disponibile e il biglietto d'oro del valore di 1.000 $ è ancora disponibile su http://www.robbylayton.com

Siamo di nuovo al lavoro sullo Spud Truck di Matt! 🛠️ Robby e la squadra si sono messi al lavoro oggi per affrontare la prossima grande fase della costruzione dello Spud Truck! Tutti al lavoro con la carpenteria, la rimozione delle ammaccature, la martellatura, l'estrazione delle chiavi, la saldatura, la smerigliatura e la carteggiatura per portare questo bestione un passo più vicino alla verniciatura. Stiamo facendo progressi significativi, ma c'è ancora una decisione importante...

Di che colore dovremmo dipingerlo? 🎨 Lasciateci le vostre idee di colore nei commenti: abbiamo bisogno del vostro aiuto per decidere!

🔧 Iscriviti per non perdere la trasformazione finale!
#RobbyLayton #SpudTruck #PaintItWhatColor

pl.title: Rozpoczęto obróbkę metalu przy ciężarówce do ziemniaków Matta!
pl.description:
Wyprzedaż onX Offroad z okazji 4 lipca wciąż trwa! Zdobądź 50% zniżki na najlepszą aplikację do mapowania szlaków, używając kodu FOJ25 na http://onxmaps.com/offroad i odblokuj ponad 650 000 mil szlaków, kempingów i narzędzi do przygód poza siecią. Jeśli się zarejestrujesz, napisz na adres merchsupport@robbylayton.com, a za każde 5 USD wydane w onX otrzymasz wstęp do rozdania nagród C10 z 1972 roku! Pieniądze z każdego zamówienia nadal trafiają na złoty bilet o wartości 1000, który wciąż jest do zdobycia na http://www.robbylayton.com

Wracamy do Spud Truck Matta! 🛠️ Robby i ekipa od razu zabrali się do pracy, ponieważ podejmujemy się kolejnego dużego etapu budowy Spud Truck! Wszyscy są na pokładzie, zajmując się obróbką metalu, usuwaniem wgnieceń, młotkowaniem, wyrywaniem kluczy, spawaniem, szlifowaniem i polerowaniem, aby zbliżyć tę bestię o krok do pomalowania. Robimy poważne postępy — ale pozostała jeszcze jedna ważna decyzja...

Jaki kolor powinniśmy pomalować? 🎨 Podzielcie się swoimi pomysłami na kolor w komentarzach — potrzebujemy Waszej pomocy w podjęciu decyzji!

🔧 Subskrybuj, aby nie przegapić ostatecznej transformacji!

es-US.title: ¡Comienza el trabajo de metal en el camión Spud de Matt!
es-US.description:
¡La oferta onX Offroad del 4 de julio sigue vigente! Consigue un 50% de descuento en la mejor app de mapas de senderos con el código FOJ25 en http://onxmaps.com/offroad y desbloquea más de 1040.000 kilómetros de senderos, zonas de acampada y herramientas para aventuras fuera de la red. Si te registras, envía un correo electrónico a merchsupport@robbylayton.com y, por cada $5 que gastes en onX, ¡te regalaremos una entrada para el sorteo del C10 del 72! El premio en efectivo de cada pedido sigue vigente; el boleto dorado de 1.000 sigue disponible en http://www.robbylayton.com.

¡Estamos de vuelta en el Spud Truck de Matt! 🛠️ ¡Robby y el equipo se pusieron manos a la obra hoy para abordar la siguiente gran fase de la construcción del Spud Truck! ¡Todos manos a la obra con metalistería, desabolladura, martillado, extracción de llaves, soldadura, pulido y lijado para que esta bestia esté un paso más cerca de la pintura! Estamos progresando mucho, pero aún queda una decisión importante...

¿De qué color la pintamos? 🎨 ¡Deja tus ideas de color en los comentarios! ¡Necesitamos tu ayuda para decidir!

snippet.title: Belton, Texas teen rescued from deadly Guadalupe River floods
snippet.description:
BELTON, Texas (KWTX) - Belton teenager Riata Schoepf was rescue by first responders on Friday after being swept away by the deadly Guadalupe River floods.

Riata went on vacation to Hunt, Texas with another family for the Fourth of July. Their hotel bordered the Guadalupe River. Her dad, Ronnie Schoepf, recalled his daughters experience being evacuated.

“She says around 2:30 or so she’s hearing loud thunder and lightning and then the next thing she knew somebody’s banging on her door telling everybody they need to get out,” Ronnie said.

Riata and her group took to their vehicles to escape the flooding, but traffic was at a standstill. Water then began to rise around their car.

snippet.title: Cyberpunk: Edgerunners 2 | Official Teaser | Netflix
snippet.description:
David is dead. But Night City lives on.
Cyberpunk: Edgerunners 2 is now in production!

Cyberpunk: Edgerunners 2 presents a new standalone 10-episode story from the world of Cyberpunk 2077— a raw chronicle of redemption and revenge. In a city that thrives in the spotlight of violence, one question remains: when the world is blinded by spectacle, what extremes do you have to go to make your story matter?

Director Kai Ikarashi (Cyberpunk: Edgerunners, SSSS.Gridman) brings a bold, cinematic vision to the series, supported by the lead character designer Kanno Ichigo (Promare, Cyberpunk: Edgerunners). They're joined by returning collaborators Masahiko Otsuka (Gurren Lagann, Promare) and Hugo Award winner Bartosz Sztybor as Showrunner, Story Writer, and Producer.

Cyberpunk: Edgerunners 2 is created in collaboration with CD PROJEKT RED and animation studio TRIGGER, with a planned release on Netflix in the future.

Stay connected, choom:
